Gateley (Holdings) (GTLY)



Gateley (Holdings)

Directorate Disclosure

RNS Number : 6548K Gateley (Holdings) PLC 11 July 2017  








11 July 2017




Gateley (Holdings) Plc
 
("Gateley" or the "Company")
 
Directorate Disclosure
 
Further to the forthcoming appointment of Suki Thompson to the Board of the Company with effect from 27th September 2017, as announced today in the preliminary results for the financial year ended 30 April 2017, the Company makes the following disclosure in respect of Schedule Two paragraph (g) of the AIM Rules for Companies: 
 
Full Name (Age): Suzanne Frances Allison Thompson (50)
 
Suki Thompson has been a director of the following companies during the five years preceding the date of this announcement:
 




Current directorships


Past directorships




The Oystercatchers Limited
Macmillan Cancer Support


The Marketing Society Limited




 
As at the date of this announcement, Suki Thompson does not hold any shares in Gateley.
 
Save as set out above, there are no are no further disclosures pursuant to Rule 17 or Schedule Two paragraph (g) of the AIM Rules for Companies.
 
- Ends -
 




Gateley (Holdings) Plc







Neil Smith, Finance Director


+44 121 234 0196




Cantor Fitzgerald Europe - Nominated adviser and broker


+44 20 7894 7000




David Foreman, Marc Milmo, Michael Reynolds (Corporate Finance)







Mark Westcott, Alex Pollen, Caspar Shand Kydd (Sales)







Arden Partners - Broker
John Llewellyn-Lloyd, Benjamin Cryer (Corporate Finance)
James Reed-Daunter (Corporate Broking)


+44 20 7614 5900




IFC Advisory - Financial PR adviser


+44 20 3053 8671




Tim Metcalfe, Graham Herring, Miles Nolan







 

